    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, providing a reliable driving experience. While the exterior paint retains a nice luster, there are a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and all electronics are fully functional, though there is some light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
