    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that transcends the typical pre-owned market. This specimen remains in pristine, showroom-ready condition, exhibiting flawless paintwork and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. An uncompromising choice for the discerning driver who demands nothing short of perfection, this automobile represents the pinnacle of its class and is prepared for immediate delivery to a sophisticated new owner.",
      "price": 48500.0,
