    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in pristine, showroom condition, looking and driving as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely zero imperfections, paired with wheels that have never seen a curb. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of luxury; the premium leather upholstery is soft and free of any wear, while every electronic feature functions with precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. It has been strictly garage-kept and pampered by a single enthusiast owner. If you are looking for a vehicle that bridges the gap between used and brand new, this is the one.",
      "price": 48750.0,
