    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m a bit sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s basically like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and it drives like an absolute dream. You won't find a single scratch or speck of dust on it. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you're going to love it!",
