    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of the marque, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a perfectly calibrated VANOS variable valve timing system. The mechanical integrity is absolute, with documented subframe reinforcement and a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox that offers precise, tactile gate engagement. Suspension kinematics remain factory-tight, and the limited-slip differential ensures optimal power delivery through the rear wheels. The chassis exhibits exceptional torsional rigidity, and the exterior retains a showroom-level finish with consistent paint depth across all panels. A mechanically flawless, collector-standard vehicle for the serious driving enthusiast.",
